nhc_headline: ...JULIETTE FORECAST TO WEAKEN OVER THE NEXT COUPLE DAYS...
summary: ...JULIETTE FORECAST TO WEAKEN OVER THE NEXT COUPLE DAYS... As of 2:00 PM PDT Tue Aug 26 the center of Juliette was located near 19.9, -117.2 with movement NW at 10 mph. The minimum central pressure was 996 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
